# New Website Project: jin-hong-me-html (V3 Standard)

## Goal Description
Create a brand new, ultra-premium website in the `jin-hong-me-html` folder. This project will serve as the "V3" evolution, incorporating all learned patterns from the Jin Hong M&E V2 overhaul but with enhanced modularity, 4K industrial aesthetics, and better structural organization.

## Proposed Changes

### [NEW] Component 1: Global Assets & Styling
- **[NEW] global.css**: Centralized design system with curated HSL color palettes, modern typography (Inter/Noto Sans SC), and smooth transition tokens.
- **[NEW] components.css**: Reusable UI components (premium cards, glassmorphism buttons, floating CTAs).
- **[NEW] 4K Sliders**: Dedicated 1600px width 4K optimized industrial imagery for the hero section.

### [NEW] Component 2: Core Pages
- **[NEW] index.html**: Ultra-premium homepage with Swiper.js, transparent-to-solid header, and deep sector highlights.
- **[NEW] Interior Pages**: Standardized [about.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/maxcoach/about.html), [services.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html/services.html), [projects.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/maxcoach/projects.html), [honors.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html/honors.html), and [contact.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/maxcoach/contact.html) with synchronized V3 layout.

